snippet.title: The Horrific Inner Workings of Nickelodeon | Corporate Casket
snippet.description:
Go to http://dailyharvest.com and enter code casket to get $25 off your first box!

Go to http://babbel.com and use promo code CASKET to get an extra 3 months of Babbel free!

Welcome to the Corporate Casket, a semiweekly series where bad businesses go to die. We will discuss any and everything from bad charities, terrible CEOs, and businesses that have a lot to hide.
